</title>
<subSubSection id="058D384E882EA1AC8C6AEFFD53191C2B" pageId="null" pageNumber="551" type="description">
<paragraph id="CFF7FE05EA48DD1AB5F458C14D3229FF" pageId="null" pageNumber="551">
<emphasis id="23F908AAC17F153DE9111C1E3E70E8DA" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="551">
<normalizedToken id="9C52CC5D608BBD06B6B02238B53F6451" originalValue="Blätter" pageId="null" pageNumber="551">Blaetter</normalizedToken>
beidseits zerstreut bis dicht behaart. 
<normalizedToken id="3DDA229AFEEEF21D0AE4EF7346E30539" originalValue="Blütenköpfe" pageId="null" pageNumber="551">Bluetenkoepfe</normalizedToken>
2,5-3 cm im Durchmesser.
</emphasis>
<normalizedToken id="75441A2261DBDD55484148713DBCC640" originalValue="Hüllblätter" pageId="null" pageNumber="551">Huellblaetter</normalizedToken>
1-1,3 cm lang, bis auf 
<normalizedToken id="F1D50DDA81AA03E9CD56A72DED8A9E1B" originalValue="½-¼" pageId="null" pageNumber="551">1/2-1/4</normalizedToken>
<normalizedToken id="FD2FF08680F6EF3B1D052B40DC70EE30" originalValue="handförmig" pageId="null" pageNumber="551">handfoermig</normalizedToken>
geteilt, dicht behaart. 
<normalizedToken id="0BA2D58BF7F4D50771D72D9130E00CBD" originalValue="Kelchröhre" pageId="null" pageNumber="551">Kelchroehre</normalizedToken>
4-5 mm lang, dicht behaart; 
<emphasis id="83ABE109ABAC7632BB85A5ECFDCD11D7" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="551">
<normalizedToken id="268CF400461C3EBDE5421F4517A9E6CC" originalValue="Kelchzähne" pageId="null" pageNumber="551">Kelchzaehne</normalizedToken>
4-5 mm lang
</emphasis>
, die obern 
<normalizedToken id="17239B55897BCD6FCA9C0DAE162437C4" originalValue="länger" pageId="null" pageNumber="551">laenger</normalizedToken>
als die untern. 
<emphasis id="376E02E6C60D6E4C6FF0F73B07AF4FA5" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="551">Krone 1,4-1,6 cm lang</emphasis>
, purpurn. - 
<normalizedToken id="7867EFFE0F51BEE4EAC60754252A169F" originalValue="Blüte" pageId="null" pageNumber="551">Bluete</normalizedToken>
: 
<normalizedToken id="C31A10DBCA75A811E5915245855363DD" originalValue="Später" pageId="null" pageNumber="551">Spaeter</normalizedToken>
<normalizedToken id="552F4121B55614BDD1B044FF68D1933C" originalValue="Frühling" pageId="null" pageNumber="551">Fruehling</normalizedToken>
und 
<normalizedToken id="C63BBD5D727A51A8A9AA7B4D38F3D812" originalValue="früher" pageId="null" pageNumber="551">frueher</normalizedToken>
Sommer.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="6E98A1F1FBCDCE6A9CF47D0FBC7C1660" pageId="null" pageNumber="551">
<emphasis id="93A47C261B080C121DD2B129572123F6" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="551">Zytologische Angaben. 2n</emphasis>
= 
<emphasis id="908D261E2C0DE226910D2B30617E335E" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="551">14:</emphasis>
Material aus den 
<normalizedToken id="2E1DA0ECFAADE6E44E9BD71FC8B2D2A8" originalValue="Südwestalpen" pageId="null" pageNumber="551">Suedwestalpen</normalizedToken>
und von den Apuanischen Alpen (Favarger 1969). 
<emphasis id="7F2C22228289B406B978EC862DF05863" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="551">2n</emphasis>
= 
<emphasis id="E29C147BB514F571F4358105AF9CD14C" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="551">28:</emphasis>
Material aus 
<normalizedToken id="3F195D7C2EECAB871F1788065EDE8199" originalValue="Südfrankreich" pageId="null" pageNumber="551">Suedfrankreich</normalizedToken>
(Caussols) (Guinochet und Logeois 1962), vom Mont Ventoux und von der 
<normalizedToken id="27F2D440F303CF051BBF8C0725AED4E3" originalValue="Dôle" pageId="null" pageNumber="551">Dole</normalizedToken>
(Favarger 1965), aus botanischen 
<normalizedToken id="5DC877BED74F90AA89B7F3E98AC72802" originalValue="Gärten" pageId="null" pageNumber="551">Gaerten</normalizedToken>
(Gilot 1965), vom Val Queyras (Westalpen) und von den 
<normalizedToken id="08F19D324C00C3160E53B50F52153074" originalValue="Pyrenäen" pageId="null" pageNumber="551">Pyrenaeen</normalizedToken>
(Favarger und 
<normalizedToken id="1EBB018F8B7A998801D7E94B716DE51A" originalValue="Küpfer" pageId="null" pageNumber="551">Kuepfer</normalizedToken>
1968), vom 
<normalizedToken id="9E0363190E7CCA824ABFDDD932BEB466" originalValue="südlichen" pageId="null" pageNumber="551">suedlichen</normalizedToken>
Jura (Favarger 1969).
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="B2B30A855543516F879ED6EDA5FD843E" pageId="null" pageNumber="551">
<emphasis id="5B347547B3967ECFA6F8F19DB6807033" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="551">Standort.</emphasis>
Kollin, montan und subalpin. Steinige, trockene, kalkreiche 
<normalizedToken id="DDD524ECD2F7C28BB404441450887AD8" originalValue="Böden" pageId="null" pageNumber="551">Boeden</normalizedToken>
in warmen Lagen. 
<normalizedToken id="37B471A60B77A070EE3D9A6C05286F4D" originalValue="Geröll" pageId="null" pageNumber="551">Geroell</normalizedToken>
, felsige 
<normalizedToken id="B1C1206A88E08B023930F49583D6004C" originalValue="Hänge" pageId="null" pageNumber="551">Haenge</normalizedToken>
, trockene Weiden.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="F3C767396F3AF50990EE3826124CCA53" pageId="null" pageNumber="551">
<emphasis id="40A5FC8CD6D6C6A5770C5EFFE4853EAC" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="551">
Verbreitung. Mittel- und 
<normalizedToken id="022DC8EF856C86BD3B1CCA19D7FDA581" originalValue="südeuropäische" pageId="null" pageNumber="551">suedeuropaeische</normalizedToken>
Gebirgspflanze
</emphasis>
(
<emphasis id="6E3AD436BEEEF619990A45ED9E82552C" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="551">westlich</emphasis>
): Nordspanische Gebirge, 
<normalizedToken id="DA0111EE66248D7C66C6BC45D641F570" originalValue="Pyrenäen" pageId="null" pageNumber="551">Pyrenaeen</normalizedToken>
, 
<normalizedToken id="43B8C2F1EA344C8AF2208577E5D22560" originalValue="Corbières" pageId="null" pageNumber="551">Corbieres</normalizedToken>
, Cevennen, Westalpen, 
<normalizedToken id="B6023C312BA48B583ECFC940B470230A" originalValue="südlicher" pageId="null" pageNumber="551">suedlicher</normalizedToken>
Jura, Apennin (
<normalizedToken id="6BC50529987F0CE38BF365CF7FB22437" originalValue="südwärts" pageId="null" pageNumber="551">suedwaerts</normalizedToken>
bis Kalabrien). - Im Gebiet: Savoyer Kalkalpen, 
<normalizedToken id="065D6A943C9D64DD67A361BF2157E7D0" originalValue="südlicher" pageId="null" pageNumber="551">suedlicher</normalizedToken>
Jura (
<normalizedToken id="BB4DD4436854DF831E3D03F7110AA7C0" originalValue="nordwärts" pageId="null" pageNumber="551">nordwaerts</normalizedToken>
bis Creux du Van und La Clusette).
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
